  UNRESOLVED RESONANCE REGION : 7.2 EV - 100 KEV                  5253 1451
    THE NEUTRON STRENGTH FUNCTIONS, S0, S1 AND S2 WERE CALCULATED 5253 1451
    WITH OPTICAL MODEL CODE CASTHY/2/.  THE OBSERVED LEVEL SPACING5253 1451
    WAS DETERMINED TO REPRODUCE THE CAPTURE CROSS SECTION         5253 1451
